Description:
Enter a posed stance and unleash a series of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;5&lt;/font&gt; quick thrust attacks with each strike dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Rapier_Flurry_Strike_1.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_thrust_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage. 

Flurry can be canceled at any time by dodging or by using another ability.

This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;
